I remember going to the science center as a kid. Our school would take us at least once a year, and my mom would take me even more. My favorite thing to look forward to was the Space Ice Cream in the gift shop, since there was no internet shopping yet, which is still a favorite of mine today (ever want to get me a simple gift? Space Ice Cream!) That's also where I learned this was little trick possible, if your object is perfectly round! This was one of the funnest things I've done at the shop in a while haha!
